snippet.title: The Deer God - Release trailer for iOS, Android, and Xbox One!
snippet.description:
The Deer God is a game about reincarnation and karma, all set in a beautiful 3d pixelized world. Launch dates - Xbox One Sept 1st
iOS Sept 3rd
